didn't approve.

41
00:02:44,372 --> 00:02:46,749
Hearing that makes me interested.

42
00:02:47,125 --> 00:02:49,210
"Things Will Be Fine
Once You Turn Thirty."

43
00:02:49,294 --> 00:02:50,587
