the menu in a restaurant.

56
00:03:33,755 --> 00:03:37,550
But I like my work
incomparably better than those things.

57
00:03:38,176 --> 00:03:40,220
This is more precious than anything else.

58
00:03:40,303 --> 00:03:42,305
And I want to do it with you.

59
00:03:43,473 --> 00:03:45,058
Not just do it, either.
I want to do it right.

60
00:03:48,853 --> 00:03:50,980
Why don't you count on me this once?

61
00:03:51,439 --> 00:03:54,192
And his attitude toward work
was sincere too.

62
00:03:54,317 --> 00:03:56,444
He's my assistant director.
She's our writer.

63
00:03:57,654 --> 00:03:58,613
Hello.

64
00:03:59,072 --> 00:04:01,991
And the crisis came right away.

65
