to protect herself.

219
00:13:52,957 --> 00:13:54,500
A smart person

220
00:13:54,708 --> 00:13:57,461
likes someone whom they can get
jealous of and respect at the same time.

221
00:14:01,632 --> 00:14:03,884
-I'm sorry.
-What did you do wrong?

222
00:14:04,093 --> 00:14:05,052
